version		2.2.3
description	This is the non-gui part of the library formerly \
		known as gnome-libs.
long_description       	This is the non-gui part of the library formerly \
			known as gnome-libs. 
maintainers	olegb@opendarwin.org
categories	gnome
platforms	darwin 
homepage	http://www.gnome.org/
